{"tid":1149213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幾時反制呀屌你】新華社：中國網民怒了","createTime":"2019-05-11T04:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T06:04:18.000Z","uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9e02d694a058435b635464447a237ca46e4c3c","tid":1149213,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nx美方已將對2000億美元中國輸美商品加征的關稅從10%上調至25%，中方對此深表遺憾，將不得不采取必要反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易摩擦再度升級，這樣的結果令人遺憾。究其原因，在於美方無視中方富有誠意的態度與行動，始終奉行&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;，漫天要價、極限施壓，這從根本上違背了相互尊重、平等互利的談判原則，從而導致摩擦升級。<br />\n<br />\n消息發出後，中國網友紛紛表達憤怒：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;美國假談判，真挑事！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n@杜子明：美國不自信，產生了貿易摩擦！輸的一定是美國！<br />\n<br />\n@路燈：對反覆無常的國家必須多長點心眼，支持反制&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n@曦：美國撕下了偽裝，是朋友就交，不是朋友也不勉強，中國，加油<br />\n<br />\n@雨花石：無論是打，還是談，都要遵守和平共處，還有一句實話名言，人不犯我，我不犯人，人若犯我，我必犯人！<br />\n<br />\n@夏天遊泳：國家核心利益必須保護，要打就打！<br />\n<br />\n還有網友認為<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們應做好自己的事&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n@醒眼：中方的反應，很有韌性，很克制，這樣好！<br />\n<br />\n@之保馬：明知是在美國的壓力下，我們要挺起腰桿來對付它！<br />\n<br />\n@風雨過後見彩虹：現在的中國不是百年前的中國，支持祖國做的決定。<br />\n<br />\n@醫者仁愛：必須反制。<br />\n<br />\n@per：堅決維護祖國利益。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gn/2019-05-10/detail-ihvhiqax7910303.d.html?wm=3049_0015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgn%2F2019-05-10%2Fdetail-ihvhiqax7910303.d.html%3Fwm%3D3049_0015&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=dbf23619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gn/2019-05-10/detail-ihvhiqax7910303.d.html?wm=3049_0015</a>"},{"pid":"936bba4f3fbefc478f741a23b931d06cc9794221","tid":1149213,"uid":156936,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"風雨過後見彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一時間就浸撚死你啦"},{"pid":"51ec9b0ad01af81a642c5c32d16fac7eb53a74b3","tid":1149213,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"俾班生蕃上FB 用GOOGLE<br />\n美國佬就知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a8aa01406fd72a74c4628096bc7f1459318d5f","tid":1149213,"uid":17765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"路燈：對反覆無常的國家必須多長點心眼，支持反制&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賤種支那種究竟係咪特登掟回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08ce155fe0ae16553563cfbc33ef0be05fb5e0e","tid":1149213,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"佢哋知發生緊乜事？即係翻牆啦，拉得"},{"pid":"fe97d16c568b40e07aff99273bdcc6c7783e29bf","tid":1149213,"uid":31780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"搵鬼怕你網民怒了咩"},{"pid":"e4b2cd33f12ba40625efb32ee677659c9671aac7","tid":1149213,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"有鬼網民,5毛網軍就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccf75fbd483d0ecb68429b9ed47adfc9082e2b1","tid":1149213,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"分分鐘成堆留言都喺同一個人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a154c056d157f4afb137c5b19e5e42f00d4db1c","tid":1149213,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:55:13.000Z","msg":"日日都有唔同order<br />\n尋日又劉副總理，辛苦了"},{"pid":"9a7449ae129b2dae3a57b5b3955d065beb90fa9a","tid":1149213,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:59:47.000Z","msg":"偉大嘅黨使出咗最強嘅武器-嘴炮<br />\n美帝又嚇傻了<br />\n支那又贏"},{"pid":"340170c893ff1f0b24f8e598d526e17705f268bd","t